{"tid":1164798,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"展示 Sony PlayStation 5 威力　載入速度快 PS4 Pro 十倍","createTime":"2019-05-21T11:00:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T03:21:42.000Z","uid":53379,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ed73c2be7537caaa507f2f4bdab6556515913a56","tid":1164798,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T11:00:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">展示 Sony PlayStation 5 威力　載入速度快 PS4 Pro 十倍</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nSony 近年越來越高調公開下一代 PlayStation 主機的資訊，除了在公開招聘人員測試新主機，及暗示新主機性價比高外，最近更公開一段實際運行對比的展示影片，對比目前的 PlayStation 4 Pro，新主機到底有多少提升。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/ps5-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2Fps5-1.jpg&h=efefed8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCEO 吉田憲一郎主持了 Sony 最新的會議，展示了「次世代 PlayStation 主機」在高性能下，壓倒性的圖像處理速度，片中PS4 Pro 載入蜘蛛俠的時間為 8 秒，但次世代主機載入時間只需要 0.8秒，提升足足 10 倍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/ps5-3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2Fps5-3.png&h=d057e2ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來新一代主機基本配備 SSD 下，載入速度得到大幅提升，有一直使用 PS4 Pro 主機的玩家，應該發現到近年的大型遊戲作品中，載入時間長得過份，差不多都要數分鐘的時間，對玩家來說真的相當漫長&hellip;。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/05/21/sonyps5/game-channel/?fbclid=IwAR0jab2fPLMOMZKGd8qlruKuwT2KWb1PideT_nn_t3DSGCWJ96saD8MsH48\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F05%2F21%2Fsonyps5%2Fgame-channel%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0jab2fPLMOMZKGd8qlruKuwT2KWb1PideT_nn_t3DSGCWJ96saD8MsH48&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbcQ0GhOv7yEvjYTsEPvBCF8%3D&h=71a28a54\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/05/21/sonyps5/game-channel/?fbclid=IwAR0jab2fPLMOMZKGd8qlruKuwT2KWb1PideT_nn_t3DSGCWJ96saD8MsH48</a>"},{"pid":"bfcdc41d5a75a7c3586b23a7a11c37fe0f62fe0e","tid":1164798,"uid":224510,"like":15,"dislike":0,"